{
  "stem": "23942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't even know where they ended.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- who knows?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was hilly in the woods, and I was even afraid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were animals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was afraid to go deep, very deep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was afraid to go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as I was walking a little bit, picking, like, blueberries or something, because I learned how to pick blueberries near-- not far from the edge.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I started picking blueberries, and I heard deep-- I heard voices.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they happened to be Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't talk to them, because I was so scared of them, I didn't know what to say.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what to say to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They was-- I think they were afraid of me, and I was afraid of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was almost-- I wasn't used to any more people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so used to being alone, that it was easier for me-- for me to walk alone through the woods than to meet a person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how-- how unused to I got to people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is-- I felt at peace by myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would walk and look up in the sky and the sun and the fields-- I mean, and the woods and the trees, and I felt they were my friends.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the people, I felt, were my enemies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't even know how to connect to my own people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't know what to say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was so unprepared to meet another human being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I just knew that I have to survive, but I didn't know how to relate to other people anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- because I was afraid, and I knew they were afraid to speak to me because I shouldn't say something in case I should be caught or something.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
